originalSql: SELECT  a.requestid, requesttimeepoch, httpmethod, resourcepath, identity.sourceip, identity.useragent, "element_at"(querystring, 'deal_code') deal_code_parameter, "element_at"(querystring, 'date_start') date_start_parameter, "element_at"(querystring, 'date_end') date_end_parameter, querystring, authorizer.principalid, responselatency, httpstatuscode, a.datehour, domainname FROM  (api_gateway_access_logs a LEFT JOIN api_gateway_execution_logs e ON (a.requestid = e.requestid))
